{"tid":27344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"校內裝cam偷拍333萬張裙底照","createTime":"2016-12-07T09:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T09:53:47.000Z","uid":34834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63c54329da737f74b804ed8c46a5291bb04fae7a","tid":27344,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"校內裝cam偷拍333萬張女教師大頭、裙底照　150萬張屬女副校大頭照　小學IT技術員還押候判 (港聞)<br />\n<br />\n於小學任職的36歲資訊科技（IT）技術員，聲稱從來未試過拍拖，對女性一直存有幻想，遂私下在校內電腦和電腦枱下安裝攝錄鏡頭，並透過黑客軟件收集女教師的大頭照、大腿照和裙底照，3年間共儲存了6名女教師逾333萬張照片，其中包括女副校長的150萬張大頭照。他今日在區院承認8項不誠實使用電腦罪，還押候判 - <br />\n<br />\nSee more at: <a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161207/s00001/1481100596836#sthash.7eVr2lFH.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161207%2Fs00001%2F1481100596836%23sthash.7eVr2lFH.dpuf&d=%2Bt1kyFtSusEBwBbR8XkNpwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=08af94e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161207%2Fs00001%2F1481100596836%23sthash.7eVr2lFH.dpuf&h=bd22a66b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161207/s00001/1481100596836#sthash.7eVr2lFH.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"91c0f03e83472c7ce7b8f6d3df3faf2ef40ee635","tid":27344,"uid":7656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:30:34.000Z","msg":"三百幾萬張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a3231f12e24d49cd19769d8715edd4de795586","tid":27344,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:30:35.000Z","msg":"333萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14f2a579fb88042736a1c4caeace2c7f5b02f45","tid":27344,"uid":34834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:32:24.000Z","msg":"邊個數的"},{"pid":"1053c2a9a11551